            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry>Type: 

                    </entry>
                    <entry>list</entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>Default: 

                    </entry>
                    <entry>N/A</entry>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> Specify the Java Virtual Machine (JVM) settings of your Java destination from the &abbrev; configuration file.</para>
    <para>For example:</para>
    <synopsis>jvm-options("-Xss1M -XX:+TraceClassLoading")</synopsis>
    <para>You can set this option only as a <link linkend="chapter-global-options">global option</link>, by adding it to the <parameter>options</parameter> statement of the syslog-ng configuration file.</para>
</topic>
